{"word":"Adullam","slug":"adullam","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Adullam</b> <a href=\"#/H5725\">H5725</a> <br/> 1. A cave near the Dead Sea<br/> - David takes refuge in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=22&verse=1'>1Sa 22:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=13'>2Sa 23:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=11&verse=15'>1Ch 11:15</a> <br/> - Reference titles of Psalm 19;57;1-11 and Psalm 19;142;1-7<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=57&verse=11'>Psa 57:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=142&verse=7'>Psa 142:7</a> <br/> 2. An ancient city of Canaan<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=38&verse=1'>Gen 38:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=12&verse=15'>Jos 12:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=15&verse=35'>Jos 15:35</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=7'>2Ch 11:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=16&chapter=11&verse=30'>Neh 11:30</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=1&verse=15'>Mic 1:15</a>"}]}